"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1599a0d7-f199-47d5-ac93-39440712fd65\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-eb9e41bc-519b-4ed6-95d0-35a6d13a8ddf\" style=\"\">싸바리 박스의 형태</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b17fee2c-3a10-4c29-a3d6-d8ea576b69a2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d05db3dd-081c-4761-b009-1f0dbd8ca0be\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1adb781-3f36-4add-9578-b0b4f4ec08f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">싸바리 박스는 크게 3가지 형태로 나뉩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4943819d-2216-407c-a1c9-eacfd944b2c8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5010f6c7-e89e-4b65-b952-8aa0b686e627\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ffeb9ce4-1652-41d0-8362-952f52d75ade\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-349d38ad-f407-48e8-a2ec-61214ca76b24\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>표지 싸바리 (표지바리)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-135debe8-74b2-4646-bb33-f709cb08a356\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80274d4b-294b-4d1e-9a1e-1b78528ae47e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-58704e00-458a-4a52-9a45-8c73b4473cc7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7548d568-2e02-4750-b4d4-fbc3fd7b880f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">표지 싸바리는 중간에 뚜껑이 합체되어 하나의 박스가 완성된 형태입니다. 윗부분에는 자석이 달리는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0c0138f3-f9f0-40a7-88c7-6aac1c97a6fd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6cd6a8e-e138-4430-99a7-a52db6fe0b77\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:488px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e74f4c44-fd23-4eed-aa37-60e830a097b9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22ab670f-24c5-4d1b-a7f7-8b25259ab6d3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f56b850f-7819-4286-9517-49ec571b5456\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 자석이 없는 형태도 있고 닫개로 만들 수도 있고 형태나 모양도 다르게 디자인할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-29da7fe9-1260-4819-a3a7-bac0868cfcef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7543977c-0e67-4f3c-9a0c-fd20415aa865\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-360d6f39-f17c-4a36-ae6f-3f898f634621\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5157ff85-0fd8-4aad-8fe9-4be0985ae593\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이 구성은 겉 싸개지와 속지로 구성됩니다. 싸개지는 150g 미만으로 자유로운 종이로 제작이 가능하며 속지는 크게 1,200g / 1,500g 두 가지 두께가 있습니다. 색상은 백색과 흑(검정) 속지가 있습니다. 물론 다른 종이를 사용할 수도 있고 특별한 종이로 조합할 수도 있지만 일반적으로는 다음과 같이 제작됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad041d66-2686-4ae8-af2e-c1dbf4c0dace\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7f4d40c7-c78e-40cb-8aee-eb7fa5799a75\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-49d1d45b-1380-4f45-a573-2da2c5578846\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-07e2c085-debc-439e-aee0-e8b908207cf9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>싸개지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0bf4ea77-6365-4c8a-b4e0-49b3ceb34202\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e916ac01-bf8e-4c7c-85c5-066dbb2ae2fc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">150g 미만의 모든 종이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34345e35-53ac-4d6b-8e49-cb9da3918ff2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9fa24063-3157-45f1-804e-30a0a8249b49\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반지/색지/펄지 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-23a926a2-876a-45b9-ab7d-7fde96c73d1c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38f68dce-1329-495b-a27f-4d10b01f834e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4dec473b-a0ee-43a6-a70a-6380ab462b62\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e650cde0-0930-4aab-99f0-44b86b25b39b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>속지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb64ed40-9b18-40a0-baf3-c32dbaafcfe3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8baf0bcf-caa1-48f8-8cf8-4f8beba32595\" style=\"color:#555555;\">1,200g / 1,500g 갱판지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-977c12c8-7e65-4262-90da-b1856c596a34\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc9be53f-4279-4ba2-b0e3-bce1a78ddea0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">백색/흑색</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4e5e2dd6-4b0f-4f47-9839-f502f6cf0f47\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1329a798-1147-4916-aebe-b7296a95bea2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f56b014f-02c6-4c7d-916a-9cfe9e8ce4eb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e0068697-e9b6-4b69-918c-8f3e6bf3896c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>설명</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d9d8a6e8-5529-4a3c-853a-3835d68fa8af\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-575b27f0-52a1-4089-a35c-c7ba25a1172d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9fd09d3c-19fa-4218-9ef5-cdcfb0b9aae2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9b32c552-1cab-4817-9db3-d1287c4b19e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 싸바리 박스는 일단 단가가 비싸며 소량 생산이 어렵습니다. 기간도 보통이 일주일이고 고급스러운 포장용 패키지로의 역할이 주된 품목입니다. 때문에 겉지에 박인쇄나 별색 인쇄로 제작되는 경우도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-5093f720-74a0-4122-aae5-45ed9333fded\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-44471040-3d54-457e-b119-f89b8443f71e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08872f64-2ed9-4f38-8770-a11ac7d03a70\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d093aa03-b3db-42b9-9db0-cda9052668e1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71b4b921-356a-4d9c-ba9f-1dd592c95f30\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ba25935-2b84-4988-b2ca-c40e580e815f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>2단 싸바리 (상/하 박스)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-11dbf2fb-683c-4f80-a444-469d4ddef148\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2e1eb910-f27d-4f01-84cb-d0a8de837de2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5216daf3-d1da-4095-8aac-cfc342c35ada\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e92bf444-edb9-4343-9b1e-96a026a83be9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2단 싸바리는 위, 아래 뚜껑이 있는 박스입니다. 그러므로 위 뚜껑 +  아래 뚜껑지로 구성됩니다. 위, 아래의 종이를 다르게 할 수도 있고 동일하게 구성할 수도 있습니다. 중간에 뚜껑이 합체되어 하나의 박스가 완성된 형태입니다. 윗부분에는 자석이 달리는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1cdf7b0b-43f0-4835-bca3-986e5ee38dc3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f4c0d007-28e0-4e8a-b5bc-5db6554a74f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8c8c2b5a-d704-43ab-b5ec-aa268a7d0fcd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af5db0c2-7cb2-4469-88e4-3f364bcf4fc2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a81a7804-a3bf-429a-bc58-b85d4327d04a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">거의 싸바리 박스는 커스텀 박스가 많습니다. 고객의 임의대로 사이즈와 종이, 인쇄 방식 등을 결정할 수 있습니다. 그렇지만 이런 이유들로 사고도 많이 나는 것이 현실입니다. 샘플 제작도 쉽지 않기 때문에 방향, 디자인, 지질, 용도에 따라 마음에 들지 않는 박스가 나올 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-89001fd5-eb69-4e07-817e-0e9aca4fb1d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6d3b667a-29e7-45ab-a6c6-33dc70abf8dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-25fdf22f-c33d-4079-ae95-7e0612501c2b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cef0594e-8daf-481c-afa7-01e6255f7687\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객님은 반드시 가격만을 보고 결정하지 마십시오. 소통과 퀄리티, 경험 등등을 고려하여 업체를 선정하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a49fd623-1ca7-4d0c-9d89-b5ccb2077270\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b69d0be2-e40a-450d-b9fd-a31f6231cb12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe876f3f-e312-4c13-ac8d-c9fa6c0c2486\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc74722b-5b25-4078-9643-1b9f746b234a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니과 거래를 안 하셔도 좋습니다. 언제든 궁금하신 사항이 있으면 문의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ceb8ee74-0c61-41c8-8640-c81836a20b5c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1acbc938-f34c-4e17-9c96-209c147e43d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-84623ddd-9ff7-42e9-8739-2a2da496b2ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8977a8bb-2011-4509-bba1-6542777b3a0d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">표지 싸바리와 마찬가지로 종이는 고객님의 선택으로 제작할 수 있습니다. 그리고 후공정으로는 박인쇄나 형압도 많이 사용하십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b905c9d1-5faa-4043-a954-dcc21a647418\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-51fc7515-6e1d-4ac1-a8c6-487e1233c08d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d13535d5-2d42-4d88-ab85-5c9c626e1fab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2030fe44-849c-4284-9c5a-566b10c96ff8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98b1de12-00db-4e8c-9921-f76f61252e95\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-718c7451-09db-4ab7-9968-177f9bd99dbb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>설명</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-036fbab0-70ed-4a8c-a174-31c00bdc72fc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-130c6048-2ee0-4847-aa22-bd4b15f733ae\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12e026d9-c87c-48d0-a46d-1d8f59126326\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5ba7e297-1c9a-47a2-a5af-c8cd6690c5ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2단 싸바리 박스는 주로 신발, 의류, 선물용으로 많이 사용됩니다.  옆쪽에 손잡이를 뚫어서 모양을 만들 수도 있고 끈으로 잘 열수 있도록 제작하기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-3f89c756-3754-470b-bfed-09f09033fa0e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6018c76e-4794-49d9-9f3d-c666339598d6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3d8f4c1-6a57-43b1-922b-0000e372ecf4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6678b825-0fdd-437d-87ec-a4a2d70f99f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f04e6216-f822-4639-abe0-796496230da6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-028741fb-3cd0-4f0a-a090-dcf5a16f984f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>3단 싸바리 (상/중/하 박스)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-31031351-ada7-4878-a1c8-3ff64d521ca7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-72592b4a-cad9-413d-8e52-18838de825c3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8d72f31-6c4d-4aea-bd10-e585230372ac\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6bfee023-66c7-4cc8-bcd1-bd1d2d772667\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3단 싸바리는 중간에 중간지가 있어서 뚜껑은 딱 맞춰서 끼우는 형태입니다. 보다 더 튼튼하고 조금 더 제품 보호용으로 튼튼한 형태입니다. 하지만 가장 비싸고 기간이나 형태도 다양합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e526158b-6d09-45a5-8b42-e452fcf8f336\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-efe76626-c01d-4a71-8a7e-30dbf11fd922\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-abc58959-4a39-4d4e-aff1-f3e632b757c4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8e64b668-b055-44de-878d-8d2db3930763\" style=\"color:#555555;\">중간에 중간지가 보이게 형태를 만들 수도 있고 중간지가 안 보이게 제작할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6576076b-ee77-4f11-82d4-2d97ba70a542\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bef288bb-d313-45f2-aef0-aa9055945cda\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d1e88db0-e4ac-4b0c-ad77-5eff821825d5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a3ef7643-abd3-4b7a-9aa1-f8cb313845b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3단 싸바리는 가장 튼튼한 형태일 수도 있고 포장재로서 가장 안전하게 제품을 보호할 수도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-74bac27b-423d-481f-b28b-b413a67931d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-806d41e7-ad02-4eff-a9fb-850df6009f9e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d843ef14-6119-4489-93b2-2c8cd1f719df\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-863210bd-8533-4e0b-8917-00bed297c40c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>설명</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ef746ca3-3320-495d-ba24-c6789739fee9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-48c5b9e5-2071-4fd5-8c8b-1166e998f7b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53c29322-6916-4bb6-abe1-560711c5d6df\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2a8bb9b1-88c0-45ea-bd7d-063de4d82e25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3단 싸바리 박스는 가장 비쌀 수 있고 또 사고가 나면 해결이 안 될 수 있으니 반드시 협력사와 긴밀한 상담을 통해 제작하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-eec7b1c6-195c-4f0f-b7ca-cdebb58670ed\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-692821e7-1740-41bd-ad25-86dd3f47e65d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c488acbc-f9bb-4ece-97d5-02491874df1f\" style=\"\">내용 정리 : 결론</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-31f01fbf-7789-4f2c-b81c-fcd466130161\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5c3670b-32e5-47e0-8f5d-dc8b7440d4d1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-87ea1610-7cf4-45fa-8085-60b809572acc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">싸바리 박스는 패키지의 결정이자 꽃입니다. 가장 비싸고 만들기도 어려우며 납기도 늦습니다. 하지만 자신의 제품을 가장 돋보이게 만들 수 있는 박스 형태이며 잘 만들면 브랜드로서의 가치도 함께 높일 수 있는 무기가 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb4cd231-6980-4d1c-a784-a7905b51500f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a49332d9-b0fc-48c0-bf2e-027ed9d5aa54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae7e07d2-e367-44ca-98ea-c32030d59e0e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bf2e13a5-791a-4b44-83db-fcc7b79f1af7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">반드시 전문 패키지 업체와 상의하세요. (주)파파스컴퍼니이 아니라도 좋습니다. 하지만 업체를 선택할 때 가장 중요한 것은 포트폴리오도 경력도 아닙니다. 고객과의 소통이 잘 되는지가 가장 중요합니다. 이점을 잘 판단하시고 업체를 선택하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223827723933/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79eba2a2-27d6-46f0-a2d7-3e8b209e30d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-31c83cab-ab04-4137-b68b-cc42c03862b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24ae41f1-f8fb-4147-9278-5edd398743cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}